### Test 1: Request without correlation ID (should generate one)
GET http://localhost:5000/weatherforecast
Accept: application/json

### Test 2: Request with correlation ID (should use provided one)
GET http://localhost:5000/weatherforecast
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-ID: my-custom-correlation-id-12345

### Test 3: Verify correlation ID in response headers
GET http://localhost:5000/weatherforecast
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-ID: test-correlation-abc-123
